    <textTemplates>
        <description>Stores the body of the email to send to EmailRecipient. To customize the email body, change the value of this text template.</description>
        <name>EmailBody</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: Segoe UI;font-size: 16px;color:black;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello {!GetRelatedAccountRecord.Name},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your provider has requested some additional information from you before your next visit. The information will be used to provide better service and save you time during your visit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;display:block; margin-left: auto; margin-right:auto; width: 40%; max-width: 350px; height:25px; color: white; background: #0176d3; border: 1px solid #c9c9c9; padding:10px; text-align: center; border-radius:5px; line-height: 25px; text-decoration: none;&quot; href=&quot;{!ExperienceCloudSiteUrl}?signature={!GenerateSignatureLink.signature}&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Complete Assessments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!$Organization.Name}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <description>Stores the body of email notifying the recipient about a new assessment that they need to complete. To customize the email body, change the body of this text template.</description>
        <name>EmailBodyTextTemplate</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dear {!GetContactRecord.Name}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;I hope this message finds you well.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;I am the Study Manager for a new clinical trial by Makana Pharma for Immunex. We are currently in the process of evaluating potential sites for our upcoming clinical trial, and we would like to invite your site to participate in this important study.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;To assess the suitability of your site, we kindly request that you complete the attached Site Feasibility Questionnaire. Your responses will provide us with valuable information regarding your site&apos;s capabilities, resources, and experience in conducting clinical trials.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Details of the Trial:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Trial Name: A Phase III Study of Immunex in Patients With Lung Cancer&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Indication: Non-squamous Nonsmall Cell Neoplasm of Lung- Phase: [Phase]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Sponsor: Makana Pharma&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Complete the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://noodles-coffee-1696.scratch.my.site.com/SiteFeasibilityQuestionnaire/s/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Site Feasibility Questionnaire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt; as per the following instructions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Instructions for Completing the Questionnaire:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Please review the attached Site Feasibility Questionnaire.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. Complete all sections of the questionnaire to the best of your ability.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. Return the completed questionnaire to us by [Submission Deadline].&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your participation in this feasibility assessment is crucial for the success of our trial, and we greatly appreciate your time and effort. Should you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to contact me directly&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Thank you,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;{!$User.FirstName} {!$User.LastName}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
